API Url : http://domain/data/mysites.json?status=active

Details:
Get the list of all my sites from "UserSite" Table using following logic:
- Get list of all sites where email is equal to the value of session email address.
- Then filter the result set based on the requested status as active / deleted. (requested status must be optional)

